title: Biden's Big Social-Spending Bill: the Good, the Bad and the Ugly
description: Seth Hanlon from the liberal Center for American Progress and Kyle Pomerleau from the conservative American Enterprise Institute discuss the Build Back Better Act, with the conversation moderated by MarketWatch's Victor Reklaitis.
